title: Sam Frost goes make-up free in a pair of skin-tight skinny jeans
title_page: Sam Frost goes make-up free in a pair of skin-tight skinny jeans | Daily Mail Online
text:
She's waking up at the crack of dawn for her new breakfast radio gig, and on Wednesday Sam Frost looked tired as she strolled the streets of Sydney suburb Paddington.
The 26-year-old appeared to have put little effort into her look as she went make-up free for the outing.
She showed off her toned legs as she rocked a pair of high-waisted skinny jeans, matching them with a peach tank top which featured a high turtle-neck collar.
Keeping it natural: Sam Frost went make-up free as she strolled the streets of Sydney on Wednesday
The first-ever Bachelorette finished off her low-key attire with a pair of beige slip-on sandals.
While she displayed her blemish free face, her two toned locks fell loosely over her shoulders.
Sam was quick to try and cover her make-up free self by adding a pair of dark shaded sunglasses.
Simple: The 26-year-old showed off her toned legs as she rocked a pair of high-waisted skinny jeans
Out and about: Her two toned locks fell loosely over her shoulders as she covered her face with a pair of dark shaded sunglasses
As she walked from her new vehicle, she flung a multi-coloured bag over her left shoulder while balancing a water bottle with her hand.
The radio host was treated to a new Mini Cooper last weekend, months after her black Hyundai was spotted parked on a suburban Bondi street with its front section smashed in.
Her boyfriend Sasha Mielczarek announced the new purchase on social media as he shared an image of herself placed in the front driver's seat while displaying a large pearly white smile.
He wrote alongside the image 'Congratulations to this dork @fro01 on the purchase of her new car!
'She was like one of them wacky inflatable tube guys at the car yard running around the show room #ishallcallhimminime,' he added.
On a mission: The radio host flung a multi-coloured bag over her left shoulder while balancing a water bottle with her hand
Brand new: Sam was treated to a new Mini Cooper last weekend, months after her black Hyundai was spotted parked on a suburban Bondi street with its front section smashed in
On Thursday evening Sam kicked off the celebrity fashion at the Witchery runway event on Thursday at Carriageworks in Sydney.
The 26-year-old stunned in an all-black ensemble which tied up tightly around her waist and accentuated her slender frame.
Best pal Sarah-Mae Amey also attended the event with the former Bachelorette.
